snippet: Andy Sullivan won his first European Tour title with a brilliant birdie on the first playoff hole as Charl Schwartzel let slip a five-shot overnight lead in a late collapse at the South African Open in Johannesburg.
abstract: Jimmy Walker and Hideki Matsuyama share third-round lead at Hyundai Tournament of Champions; other golf scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Andy Sullivan won his first European Tour title with a brilliant birdie on the first playoff hole as Charl Schwartzel let slip a five-shot overnight lead in a late collapse at the South African Open in Johannesburg.
